@startuml
title Interpreter

skinparam legendBackgroundColor #f9f9f9
skinparam legendBorderColor #999999

legend right
**Intent**: Define a grammar and an interpreter to evaluate expressions in the language.

**Use when**: Simple grammars; frequent new sentences; parse trees.

**Key participants**: AbstractExpression, TerminalExpression, NonterminalExpression, Context.
endlegend

class Context {
  +lookup(symbol:String)
}

interface AbstractExpression {
  +interpret(ctx: Context)
}

class TerminalExpression
class NonterminalExpression {
  -expressions : List<AbstractExpression>
  +interpret(ctx: Context)
}

AbstractExpression <|.. TerminalExpression
AbstractExpression <|.. NonterminalExpression
NonterminalExpression *-- AbstractExpression
@enduml